            "metadata": {
                "abstract": "We present Omics Fusion, a new web-based platform for integrative analysis of omics data. Omics Fusion provides a collection of new and established agents and visualization methods to support researchers in exploring omics data, validating results or understanding how to adjust experiments in order to make new discoveries. It is easily extendible and new visualization methods are added continuously. It is available for free under: https://fusion.cebitec.uni-bielefeld.de/.",
